Borsellino and Mr Giovani Falcone, writes Robert Graham in Rome. Mr Madonia
has been wanted by police since 1984. The Madonia family controls the city
of Gela in Sicily. Yesterday, police said Mr Madonia was probably number two
in the Cosa Nostra hierarchy.
