FT  05 SEP 92 / UK Company News: Pittencrieff beats low US oil prices
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Despite the recession and depressed oil and gas prices in the US,
Pittencrieff increased its pre-tax profit by 42 per cent in the first half
of 1992.
The group, also engaged in the communications business, saw turnover jump
from Pounds 4.19m to Pounds 7.09m. The profit was up from Pounds 1.55m to
