intended to launch a second Aircraft Lease Portfolio Securitisation (Alps)
fund 'early in the autumn'. The fund would have a value of about Dollars
750m.
A third fund would follow by March 1993.
These two issues follow the ground-breaking Dollars 500m Alps issue by the
Irish company in June this year.
